name: Urashima Taro
skill: Deals 3530/4328 DMG to current target, with a high chance of inflicting Stun.

additional_data.description: A fisherman who met a sad fate after rescuing a tortured turtle. At first he regretted his decision to open the magical box given to him by Princess Oto, but then he decided to make the most of what happened and write a memoir about his time in the Palace of the Dragon God. Considered young adult fiction by today's standards, it was met with great critical and popular acclaim, making him quite famous. It also helped him amass a small fortune, according to some sources.
additional_data.how_to_acquire:
◦ Limited Jewel Summon 14/06/17- 05/07/2017
◦ Trade at Exchange for 50 Mochi 02/07/2017 - 05/07/2017
additional_data.notes_and_trivia:
◦ Increases the total Event Points gained by 33% during the "Coastal Calamity - Tanabata Beach Contest" event.
◦ The effect increases with the number of limit breaks. (33% → 49.75% → 66.5% → 83.25% → 100%)
◦ Summon rate increased until 14/06/17- 05/07/2017

summon: "The name's Urashima. Nice to meet you!"
